{"word":"χωλεύω","slug":"χωλεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χωλεύω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be</i> or <i>become lame, to halt, limp</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to make lame</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be lame</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>: generally, <i>to be maimed</i> or <i>imperfect</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}